E '''''Kandela grandi na Dhaka di 2010''' tawata un candela na e ciudad di Dhaka, Bangladesh, riba 3 di juni 2010 cu a mata por lo menos 100 hende.<ref name="BBC">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/world/south_asia/10232918.stm|title=Bangladeshi housing-block fire kills dozens|date=3 June 2010|work=[[BBC News]]|publisher=[[British Broadcasting Corporation]]|accessdate=3 June 2010}}</ref>

== Causa ==

Esaki a pasa ora e tranformator electrico a explota.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE65257K20100603|title=At least 40 dead in Bangladesh fire|date=3 June 2010|work=[[Reuters]]|accessdate=3 June 2010}}</ref> Departamento di Bombero a bisa cu e canela a wordo  activa door un kimico y otro producto flamabel stiwa den e tienda. E luga cu tawata cerca di e zona recidencial a haci dificil pa e bombero sofoca e vlam.

== Morto y herido ==

E candela aki a pega candela na otro edificio den e districto di Nimtoli.<ref name="BBC"/> y tawatin recidencia trapa den e apartamento.<ref name="AFP">{{cite news|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5hTxCoG19dN9NCBnfJoaRt2z3HIFg|title=85 dead, 100 injured in Bangladesh blaze: police|date=3 June 2010|work=AFP|accessdate=3 June 2010}}</ref>E candela a cunsa 10.30 pm y a dura pa 3 ora largo.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2010/jun/04/dhaka-fire-deaths|title=Dhaka fire kills at least 77, injures 100|last=Jones|first=Alice|date=4 June 2010|work=[[The Guardian]]|accessdate=3 June 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://uk.news.yahoo.com/18/20100603/twl-87-dead-100-injured-in-bangladesh-bl-5aa7274.html|title=87 dead, 100 injured in Bangladesh blaze: police|date=3 June 2010|work=Yahoo! News|accessdate=3 June 2010}}</ref> Mas di 100 hende a muri y mas di 100 tawata seriamente herida.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=127410319|title=Bangladesh Fire Kills Up To 104, Injures Over 100|date=3 June 2010|work=[[National Public Radio]]|accessdate=4 June 2010}}</ref>   E candela aki a afecta un fiesta di bruid na unda e victima a bay paniek.<ref name="AFP"/>
Na a trata e heridonan na e Dhaka Medical College Hospital, cu a lucha pa atende e gran cantidad di pashent cu a sufri di kimadura y inhalacion di humo.<ref name="TOI">{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/Midnight-fire-kills-at-least-77-in-Bangladesh-capital--/articleshow/6009323.cms|title=Midnight-fire kills at least 77 in Bangladesh capital|date=4 June 2010|work=[[The Times of India]]|accessdate=3 June 2010}}</ref><ref name="AFP"/><ref name="AFP"/>Segun e dokter di e hospital, e  mayoria  di henden cu a muri tawata mas tanto pa inhalacion di humo na luga di kimadura.<ref name="BBC"/>


